Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.12,0:00:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Excuse me. This is Nippon Transport. \NI've brought a delivery. {\i0}{the very first line is with a dropout, off to a great start}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.79,0:00:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you. We'll let you in.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.13,0:00:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi, take care of it, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.64,0:00:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.78,0:00:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.91,0:00:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's something tasty.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.32,0:00:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you as always.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.83,0:00:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.55,0:00:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's inside?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.28,0:00:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? A tape?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.21,0:01:05.46,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here are your orders. This investigation concerns the recent surge in kidnappings of beautiful young women.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.46,0:01:10.98,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to intel, there are rumors that the Taikun Country Embassy is somehow involved. {\i0}{??? taikun means "monarch", and it's not a realistic country name either, but it has to be a proper name so idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.98,0:01:13.52,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Proceed with extreme caution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.52,0:01:17.72,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I doubt you girls would let yourselves get kidnapped, but still, be careful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.23,0:01:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that attitude?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.72,0:01:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he mean we wouldn't get kidnapped? {implying they're ugly?}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.96,0:01:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Chief Haji for you. {haji? hagi? haji means "shame/embarrassment" but this sounds like a proper name?}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.24,0:01:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, time to get to work.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.71,0:01:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Taikun Embassy \Nis that gloomy building, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.36,0:01:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it totally gives off a creepy vibe.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.29,0:01:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you two go scout the area. \NIf you find anything, contact me immediately.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.38,0:01:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check elsewhere in the meantime.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.17,0:01:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Miki.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.46,0:01:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that, Megumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.59,0:01:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of place is an embassy anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.63,0:01:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me, I don't really know either. \NProbably where important foreign people stay.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.36,0:01:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Would people like that really kidnap girls?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.69,0:02:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But important people usually do wild stuff, \Nand they're fine with deceiving others.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's depressing.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.76,0:02:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's probably it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.70,0:02:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It really does look secretive.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.22,0:02:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi, what's the plan?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.94,0:02:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wait until it gets dark. \NThen we'll sneak in.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.54,0:02:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.31,0:02:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is super suspicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.62,0:02:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lookouts.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go straight from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.67,0:03:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The straightest path \Nisn't always the shortest. {lit: if you hurry, go around - usually, it's a proverb that means "more haste, less speed; slow and steady wins the race​" - but here she means it literally "the fastest way is to actually go around the building"}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep watch around the perimeter.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.71,0:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.69,0:03:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Megumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumors were true.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.89,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So they really were the ones behind it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Headquarters?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.89,0:04:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Saiko. \NPut me through to the Chief.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's me. What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.85,0:04:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi and Miki went to the Taikun Embassy \Nand we haven't heard from them since.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Understood. I'll head over right away too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.23,0:04:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should get to the embassy as fast as possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.97,0:04:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.50,0:04:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I get why people say \Nthere are alligators living in the sewers.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.46,0:04:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jackpot.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.64,0:05:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oopsie-daisy. Alright, \Nnow where could they be held?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.14,0:06:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, shall we get started?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.69,0:06:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of reactions we'll get. \NLooking forward to it, ladies.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.81,0:06:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Tickles, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.36,0:06:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It tickles so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.03,0:07:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It tickles, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop... it tickles!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.11,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop... Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.96,0:07:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna feel even better now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{?? onegai?}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.44,0:09:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No... make it stop... please!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{mou yame?}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{dame?}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No more...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... mercy!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.88,0:12:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's this young lady's turn.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.06,0:12:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take good care of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.46,0:12:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long you can endure.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... what's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.78,0:12:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.46,0:12:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.44,0:12:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.46,0:12:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No! Not there!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? Does it tickle?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please, make it stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.16,0:13:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.08,0:13:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.38,0:13:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Make her suffer more.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.21,0:13:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like this, \Nthen tell us why you sneaked in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.01,0:13:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please, make it stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.30,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything. \NI can't say anything...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.27,0:13:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please, stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Have mercy, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.64,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... can't take it! {kurushi = to suffer - idk what she means or what to call it in EN}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.19,0:13:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just stop right there, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.19,0:13:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only getting started.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.62,0:13:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Make her suffer more.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.13,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No... N-No, stop already...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.92,0:14:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.03,0:14:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No more... please! \NPlease stop this! I can't take it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No... more...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.65,0:14:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me... please!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... no! Make it stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.59,0:15:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.40,0:15:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, ready to confess yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.76,0:15:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Absolutely not! Never!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.69,0:15:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, please, make it stop... no more!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.21,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I can't... anymore...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.62,0:15:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have mercy... \NPlease... make it stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.30,0:16:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.42,0:16:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts... please!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.98,0:16:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... I really don't know anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.97,0:16:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, please...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.51,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna die! You've gotta stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.18,0:16:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to talk a little yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.85,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear... I don't know anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.46,0:16:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Confess quickly. \NIt's for your own good.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.48,0:16:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'm really gonna die...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.66,0:16:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... at my limit...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.74,0:16:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, forgive me...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, please...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.52,0:17:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. We've still got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.93,0:17:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Does it feel good?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please... I'm...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please, I c-can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.04,0:17:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, no more...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.28,0:17:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, somebody...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.50,0:17:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. We're still just getting started.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.50,0:17:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.69,0:18:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No more...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... no more!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.91,0:18:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, missy, the sooner you confess, the better.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.76,0:18:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No more... no...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.33,0:18:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Missy, we won't stop until you confess.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth... I swear!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.78,0:18:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you, make it stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.93,0:19:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't confess, we can't stop.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.32,0:19:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please, I can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.19,0:19:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.93,0:19:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.39,0:19:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore! Please, spare me! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.08,0:19:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.15,0:19:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Ready to confess yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.72,0:19:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm losing it...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.99,0:19:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going insane! No! \NPlease, make it stop! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.75,0:19:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... please...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.96,0:19:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you won't confess, we can't stop yet.} We can't stop unless you confess.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.88,0:19:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never talk! Absolutely never!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.22,0:20:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a stubborn young lady.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you! Make it stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.10,0:20:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.41,0:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{We're only starting. \NI can't go easy on you then.} We've only just begun. It'll only get worse.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.24,0:20:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... no...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.29,0:20:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now then, next up the vibrator is going \Nto set your bodies on fire from inside out.} The next step: the vibrator is going to set \N your bodies on fire from the inside out.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.21,0:21:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? Feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.66,0:21:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{ii? good? yes?}
