Dialogue: 10,0:24:56.77,0:24:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:44.13,0:26:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this... so cruel!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:48.92,0:26:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:50.80,0:26:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself, Megumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:54.76,0:26:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore... \NI've had enough... no more!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:00.16,0:27:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? \NYou have to stay strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:03.91,0:27:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi and Miki, get out of here first \Nand call for backup at headquarters.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:09.74,0:27:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You two escape quickly too.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:15.37,0:27:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, sis? {aneki - female variant of aniki - kinda means she's senior among them}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:16.78,0:27:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay and investigate a little more.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:18.78,0:27:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:19.58,0:27:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm heading out. Be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:22.14,0:27:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:56.99,0:27:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to, young lady?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:59.82,0:28:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had the pleasure \Nof seeing your magnificent body.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:03.44,0:28:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all truly honored \Nto witness such a spectacle.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:08.67,0:28:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, we'll help you enjoy yourself thoroughly. Are you prepared?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:14.51,0:28:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we intend to have \Nplenty of fun ourselves as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:22.00,0:28:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But before the fun begins, \Ncould you answer one question?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:28.48,0:28:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We already know you're a spy, but your client's identity is still unknown.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:35.97,0:28:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like you to tell us that.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:38.36,0:28:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd tell you something like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:41.61,0:28:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get these chains off me.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:43.76,0:28:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Only after you answer my question.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:47.29,0:28:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, won't you tell me who your client is?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:50.85,0:28:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This little game of ours would cause problems \Nif it became public, you see. {meaning they'd be in trouble if it became public knowledge that they kidnap and tickle-torture women}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:53.74,0:28:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnapping girls is just a game to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:56.64,0:28:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:58.07,0:29:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously! Kidnapping plus sexual assault — \Nthis is a textbook crime.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:03.42,0:29:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Say whatever you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:05.32,0:29:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all enjoying this with mutual consent.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:08.99,0:29:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, we'll be having you \Njoin in the fun too.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:12.68,0:29:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Moron!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:13.94,0:29:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do this, you'll regret it like hell later.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:16.98,0:29:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, quite a feisty young lady.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:20.67,0:29:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please enjoy yourself \Nto the point of death.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:24.79,0:29:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have some fun. \NTickle torture start!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:28.44,0:29:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir.
