Dialogue: 10,0:38:01.94,0:38:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Hands up!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:06.42,0:38:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm placing all three of you under arrest \Nfor kidnapping and rape.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:24.58,0:38:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Big sis, are you okay? Hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:28.13,0:38:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko, I was so worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:30.66,0:38:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I started making arrangements \Nright after I got your call,
Dialogue: 10,0:38:33.56,0:38:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but everyone was busy \Nso it didn't go as smoothly as I'd hoped.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:37.81,0:38:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. \NWell, since everyone made it out safely,
Dialogue: 10,0:38:41.35,0:38:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,let's just say all's well that ends well...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:51.70,0:38:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Chief.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:55.54,0:39:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so embarrassing. \NYou saw me in such a humiliating state, Chief.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:00.51,0:39:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't tell them a single word about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:03.26,0:39:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I held out through the tickling \Nand the vibrator torture.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:07.33,0:39:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I acknowledge that. But you got quite wet, \Ndidn't you? That was quite the vibrator.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:14.04,0:39:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I look, the more impressive it is. \NI almost want to try it myself. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:19.76,0:39:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey sis, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:21.84,0:39:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, don't get so down about it. {disappointed}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:24.46,0:39:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chief saw all my most private parts!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:28.25,0:39:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls got lucky.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:29.83,0:39:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "we got lucky"?
